org.smtlib.ext

Class C_what

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smtlib.impl.Command
      • org.smtlib.ext.C_what
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iwhat, IAccept, ICommand, IPos.IPosable

    public class C_what
extends Command
implements Iwhat
    Implements the non-standard what command. This command takes an arbitrary number of arguments, all Symbols, and prints the Sort of each one; if there are no arguments, the command prints all of the defined ids. FIXME - the output is not in SExpr form.
    Author:
    David R. Cok
